spec.name: FASTQFETCHER:FASTQ_MULTIQC:FASTQC (SRR36447178)
spec.script:
printf "%s %s\n" SRR36447178.fastq.gz SRR36447178.gz | while read old_name new_name; do
        [ -f "${new_name}" ] || ln -s $old_name $new_name
    done

    fastqc \
        --quiet \
        --threads 6 \
        --memory 1365.3333333333 \
        SRR36447178.gz

    cat <<-END_VERSIONS > versions.yml
    "FASTQFETCHER:FASTQ_MULTIQC:FASTQC":
        fastqc: $(echo $(fastqc --version) | sed '/FastQC v/!d; s/.*v//' )
    END_VERSIONS
